overview: Stepmother Jelena Jensen promises to help teen Jenna J. Ross regain her position on the cheer team. Stepmom Mindi Mink helps her teen stepdaughter Bobbi Dylan shoot a racy video to get the attention of her favorite boy band. MILF Jaclyn Taylor books a house call with sex therapist Allie Haze, so that her daughter-in-law Gina Valentina can get pregnant. Teen Jasmine Summers chooses to live with her stepmother Elexis Monroe when her parents get into a fight. Newly wed psychologist Jelena Jensen finally meets her stepdaughter Kenna James.
title: My Mom's Tits
